Introduction

Kim Byeongkwan, formerly known as Jason, is a South Korean singer under Beat Interactive. He is a member of the boy group A.C.E.

In 2017, Kim Byeongkwan, and his fellow members Wow and Donghun, became a contestant on the JTBC's new survival show MIXNINE. He made it to the final lineup after achieving 4th place, but unfortunately, after much discussion, it was decided the MIXNINE group would not debut.
